23-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T15:48:11-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T15:48:11-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊斥资 17 亿美元收购 iRobot 的交易遭到一些反对</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;由重叠线条组成的橙色、黑色和棕褐色背景上亚马逊文字标记的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HTyoMNDWNqCHjLl7IyWFUHPW5U4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72907001/acastro_STK103__03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Vju2jv&quot;>;欧盟监管机构已向亚马逊发出一份反对声明，反对该公司以 17 亿美元收购 Roomba 制造商 iRobot 的提议。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_23_5990&quot;>;一份新闻稿&lt;/a>;中，欧盟委员会表示，它“已告知亚马逊其初步观点：其拟收购 iRobot 可能会限制机器人吸尘器市场的竞争。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uqiKB9&quot;>;亚马逊于 2022 年 8 月宣布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2022/8/5/23293349/amazon-acquires-irobot-roomba-robot-vacuums&quot;>;计划收购 iRobot&lt;/a>;。此后，拟议的收购受到了监管机构的审查，欧盟委员会透露了一项调查&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/6/23628636/eu-regulators-amazon-irobot-roomba-收购调查&quot;>;2023 年 7 月&lt;/a>;。英国监管机构审查了该交易&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gov.uk/government/news/amazon-s-purchase-of-roomba-maker-cleared-by-cma&quot;>;但于 6 月份批准了&lt; /a>;.联邦贸易委员会要求亚马逊和 iRobot &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2022/09/20/tech/roomba-amazon-ftc-investigation/index.html&quot;>;提供有关该交易的信息&lt; /a>; 2022 年 9 月。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tDYnKW&quot;>;欧洲...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/ 27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T15:45:18-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T15:45:18-05:00</updated><title>网络星期一最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;网络星期一用手机购物的人的明亮彩色矢量插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dsf1GiP4Phn-ykVroKnHQ8R1ieQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72905335/236878_CYBER_WEEK_DEALS_AFernandez.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hw6L8a&quot; >;长假周末后的星期一毫无乐趣，除非您想省钱。如果您错过了黑色星期五的所有超值优惠，那么“网络星期一”为您提供了在假期前节省大量现金的又一个机会。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;idm7Ct&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;bZLjoB&quot;>;例如，您仍然可以在购买许多受欢迎的礼物时获得大幅折扣，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort -Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B0CCZ1L489?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. amazon.com/Introducing-sound-compact-speaker-Lavender/dp/B09ZXJDSL5/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Amazon 的 Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href =“https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/roam”rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Sonos Roam&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Kindle-Paperwhite-adjustable-Ad-Supported/dp/B08KTZ8249/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Kindle Paperwhite&lt;/a>;。还有许多其他类型的小工具的优惠，包括手机、智能手表、耳机、充电器、玩具和各种配件。并非所有的优惠都是黑色星期五的剩菜。其他小工具现在甚至更便宜，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation/dp/B07K1WWBJK?tag=theverge